data.value: Copy and paste buttons above into left panel - Text is HP - Fore colour is green for vines - Set backround image to - Create and image list from toolbox (You can change the image resolution (200x200 is best for right now)) - Input images in breakage order 0 -> hp - 1 - Assign button to image list - Panel backround image with be game backround image - Level will be saved to the folder on the right - Be confident in your level before you start a new one, there is currently no way to edit xml levels(in prog)
